{"tid":922334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獲6.6萬票　梁天琦豪言「泛民建制本土　今後三分天下」","createTime":"2018-11-30T09:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T10:01:37.000Z","uid":50457,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d876c1d355cfb5b8788e20d42d34c649694a2ac","tid":922334,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:40:54.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】本土民主前線梁天琦在新界東補選中取得6.6萬票，他認為今次選舉結果顯示，香港政治不再是泛民、建制二元對立，「而係三足鼎立」，又明言本土派會整裝待發，9月進軍政治圈，強調理念不同，拒與泛民協調。而補選中力撐梁的熱血公民及普羅政治學苑，昨更率先宣佈9月派人參選立法會。佔中三子之一的陳健民認為，補選結果反映特首梁振英想以強硬政策踢走泛民，反而令本土力量冒起。<br />\n記者：陳雪玲 梁佩珊<br />\n<br />\n年僅24歲的港大生梁天琦首度參選立法會，他在初一旺角騷亂一役被捕後，立即成為選戰焦點。梁天琦公佈選舉結果後稱，過往政府、政黨，以至主流傳媒不斷描繪為暴徒的人，在新東補選後證明，他們已成是一股不可忽視的力量，今後將是「建制派、泛民主派、本土派，三分天下」、「今日我哋攞到6.6萬人授權，證明主流絕對唔係大晒」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160301/19511514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160301%2F19511514&d=x6QnK7izEOu77SqpzK8VetibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=487f2781\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160301%2F19511514&h=78a589e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160301/19511514</a><br />\n<br />\n兩次補選比大家睇到三原色分立<br />\n本土派已獨立於泛民，共狗<br />\n可憐天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1dea8ac128d2ee408e59899f68c0d2149f67ae4","tid":922334,"uid":66839,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"笑死人咩， 未入閘都被人DQ哂啦"},{"pid":"eeb00b7fa7485573d9f2dab9b6855bff8e5fcdb2","tid":922334,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:42:34.000Z","msg":"2016-03-01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03392167318687b177d95362946ec222435c309c","tid":922334,"uid":221171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:45:37.000Z","msg":"冇dq嘅話 佢冇講野wo<br />\n(利申: 六萬其中一票)"},{"pid":"ae8cb291a8786c20fc56f4a0db779de988eaf61c","tid":922334,"uid":221171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03392167318687b177d95362946ec222435c309c","tid":922334,"uid":221171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:45:37.000Z","msg":"冇dq嘅話 佢冇講野wo<br />\n(利申: 六萬其中一票)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:45:53.000Z","msg":"冇講錯*"},{"pid":"1fe44ddf5b55e72c55bfc149c548a0b8c45bbd57","tid":922334,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n所以泛民獨裁係唔會吸到本土派嘅票"},{"pid":"509bda84c652a3c32a3976e49d77887ecb34ce30","tid":922334,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:50:36.000Z","msg":"6萬計少左 大把人當時含撚投楊ONQ"},{"pid":"58caf6de24f129b496c72b90bd5101daa7b15635","tid":922334,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"509bda84c652a3c32a3976e49d77887ecb34ce30","tid":922334,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:50:36.000Z","msg":"6萬計少左 大把人當時含撚投楊ONQ"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"係，潛在本土的選民遠遠大過呢個數<br />\n<br />\n呢兩次補正正講，即使DQ晒所有本土派侯選人，都唔會令人轉陣型"}]}